name: Nazi Enemy Bumper Pack
description: This is a monster resource pack for Wolfenstein themed projects. It contains 7 different SS Nazi soldiers: Pistol Infantry Pistol NCO Pistol Officer Pistol Officer with trenchcoat Rifle Infantry Machinegun Infantry Machinegun NCO Machinegun Officer If you use these in your own project, please contact me I would love to try it out :) Please note that attack and pain frames do not have full rotations, this should not be a problem in single player but may be noticeable with more players.
